==Xcite Center==
The Xcite Center is an event center at Parx that hosts concerts, entertainment performances, comedy acts, and boxing and MMA matches. All shows require audience members to be age 21 or older. The event center has an area of and seats over 1,500 people. The Xcite Center opened on January 13, 2018, with a sold-out concert by Chicago.

==Physical attributes==
The track has a dirt oval and a 7 furlong - - turf oval.

